iMates02cropped.png", "id": "398942312562424", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75404387_398942315895757_5737287799332143666_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KObAKaZbx4cQ7kNvgERlxDF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYANrA6LQEd9HDuo6ScR9Pm_OaXtFf3eKVuIHVzqxHuOPA&oe=67236BBB"}, {"file_name": "VRShogiMates03cropped.png", "id": "337914812432265", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974774_337914815765598_1762840369253842605_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OIVXbOmHBDEQ7kNvgHYtGN9&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCQDs1YlSKTbga2FcUANInVTRgVL0rgSwY9wYd2P8TLbA&oe=67236621"}, {"file_name": "VRShogiMates04cropped.png", "id": "367552249204365", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031624_367552252537698_6058304213158592905_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LHYsnjarHjsQ7kNvgG2q_0-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAVmh7HkRO7m5e1Ya33uL5vtCzJyFrjr1Wf3n1Zk2wHPg&oe=67235C65"}, {"file_name": "Chess cropped.png", "id": "902765531159168", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984463_902765534492501_3956653358745274292_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PAMA3I8E_q0Q7kNvgHmz_2a&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBUjUFfagM-oNI-spnGG8jikwrBcpE0YJJy4O9EeSKO0A&oe=67235763"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TrailerScreenshot cropped.png", "id": "717849803637730", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982545_717849806971063_8753740338935084738_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=c66TA9O6jg4Q7kNvgFfjAKd&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCh9cCutURL5f4xJ4bXHU5_WLR2YMG4sN2TNcBa_Ki38A&oe=6723713B"}, "display_name": "VRShogiMates", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to VRShogiMates, your gateway to a captivating virtual realm of classic board games! As a solo developer's passion project, this app delivers an unparalleled experience featuring Shogi, Chu Shogi, Chess, Xiangqi, and the unique Gungi from Hunter X Hunter.\n\nMultiplayer Mode:\nChallenge opponents worldwide in real-time or correspondence matches. Whether facing friends or discovering new adversaries, the global multiplayer functionality ensures a dynamic and engaging experience.\n\nHow to play:\nNew to these intricate games? No problem! VRShogiMates provides comprehensive rules, instructions, and a game record for each game type to help you learn. Explore the rules, grasp essential strategies, and elevate your skills!\n\nRegular Updates and Support:\nMy commitment doesn't end at launch. Expect continuous updates, bug fixes, performance enhancements, and exciting new features driven by valuable feedback from us.\n\nUnique Highlights:\nVenture into the unexplored VR realms of Shogi, Chu Shogi, Xiangqi, and Gungi - experiences currently not offered by any other VR app on the market! The last game type, Gungi, brings a touch of fantasy to your gaming repertoire. It\u2019s refreshingly different from other board games, check it out!\n\nEmbark on this virtual journey, where tradition meets innovation, and every move is a step towards victory. VRShogiMates is not just a game; it's a portal to a world where strategy, competition, and community converge. Join us and redefine your board gaming experience!", "short_description": "Dive into the immersive world of board games with VRShogiMates! Play Shogi, Chu Shogi, Chess, Xiangqi, and Gungi in a stunning virtual environment. Challenge friends globally in real-time or turn-based multiplayer. Learn the rules for all the games, while enjoying regular updates for an ever-evolving gaming experience.\n\nInternet connection is required to play. (For now)\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://app.websitepolicies.com/policies/view/a41733bc", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name":